data.description: Wonderful Bright open and airy 4 bedroom Ranch style home in the heart of Thornton. Family room with Luxury Vinyl wide wood Plank flooring and built in Entertainment area. Open Kitchen with the wood plank flooring, Farm sink and hood above the Oven/stove. Nice Dining area off the Kitchen. Spacious Primary bedroom with frosted glass Farm door, ensuite private bathroom, large walk in closet and charming double French Doors to the exterior. New Interior paint, updated doors and light fixtures, new water heater. Nice covered Front Porch, fenced backyard and check out the oversized 2 car garage which is rare for the area. Near highways, public transit, a commuters dream!
